subject: Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Penn trounced Princeton Tuesday night in its last tuneup for its third consecutive N.C.A.A. tournament appearance. For Princeton, it was just another double-digit loss in a dismal season.
